<manpage>
    <sample url="sdk\operating_system\crt\libc\io\_chsize">_chsize</sample>
    <title> _chsize</title>
    <volume>C 运行库函数</volume>
    <routine_idx> io_idx.htm </routine_idx>

    <description>
        <para>改变文件的大小。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>int</return_val>
        <func_name>_chsize</func_name>
        <parameters>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>int</param_type>
                <param_name>handle</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>打开文件的句柄</para>
                </param_note>
            </func_param>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>long</param_type>
                <param_name>size</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>文件的新的长度，以字节为单位</para>
                </param_note>
            </func_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

    <return>
        <para>如果成功改变文件的大小，则返回0；出错则返回-１，将错误号(errno)设置为下列常量之一：</para>
        <table>
    	    <th>
    	        <td>错误号</td>
    	        <td>描述</td>
    	    </th>
            <tr>
                <td>EACCES</td>
                <td>指定文件被锁定，不能进行该操作</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>EBADF</td>
                <td>指定文件为只读文件，或者句柄是非法的</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>ENOSPC</td>
                <td>设备上没有足够剩余空间进行此操作</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
               <td>EINVAL</td>
               <td>文件的新长度(参数size)应该大于0</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </return>

    <remarks>
        <para>根据参数size指定的长度，_chsize函数扩展或截短与句柄handle向关联的文件。该文件必须打开，并且是可写模式。当文件被扩展时，文件的扩展部分将添加空字符（“\0”）。如果文件被截短，从被截短的文件末尾到原始文件长度部分的数据将全部丢失。</para>
    </remarks>

    <requirements>
        <routine>
            <routine_name>_chsize</routine_name>
            <headerfile>io.h</headerfile>
            <compatibility>Windows 2000, Elastos </compatibility>
        </routine>
    </requirements>

    <example>
<pre>
//==========================================================================
// Copyright (c) 2000-2004,  Elastos, Inc.  All Rights Reserved.
//==========================================================================

/* _chsize.cpp:This program uses _filelength to report the size
 * of a file before and after modifying it with _chsize.
 */

#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;
#include &lt;io.h&gt;
#include &lt;stat.h&gt;
#include &lt;fcntl.h&gt;

int main()
{
    int fh = 0, result = 0;

    /* Open a file */
    if ((fh = _open(&quot;data&quot;, _O_RDWR | _O_CREAT, _S_IREAD
                         | _S_IWRITE))  != -1) {
        printf(&quot;File length before: %ld\n&quot;, _filelength(fh));
        if ((result = _chsize(fh, 329678)) == 0)
            printf(&quot;Size successfully changed\n&quot;);
        else
            printf(&quot;Problem in changing the size\n&quot;);
        printf(&quot;File length after:  %ld\n&quot;, _filelength(fh));
        _close(fh);
    }

    return 0;
}
</pre>
    </example>
<result>
File length before: 0
Size successfully changed
File length after:  329678
</result>

    

